h2. Release Notes - Karaf - Version 2.1.2

This release of Apache Karaf is based off of the 2.1.x series branch, representing an update to Apache Karaf 2.1.1. It contains several bug fixes identified in the prior release, and updates the pax-url version. For more detail please see the change log below.

h3. Bug
    * [KARAF-262|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-262] - The command admin create new instance cannot create good script in bash language on cygwin
    * [KARAF-270|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-270] - karaf-service scripts tries to create "data" directory in wrong location 
    * [KARAF-273|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-273] - java.lang.NullPointerException: Inflater has been closed
    * [KARAF-277|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-277] - The bin/client script does not work anymore
    * [KARAF-284|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-284] - Remove snapshot dependency on org.apache.karaf.shell.console in archetypes/command/src/main/resources/archetype-resources/pom.xml
    * [KARAF-285|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-285] - The bin/shell script should not read the input stream when a command is passed
    * [KARAF-286|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-286] - When running in the plain shell console (using bin/shell), tab completion prints lots of exceptions
    * [KARAF-292|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-292] - Maven filtering issue for Windows batch files in kit

h3. Task
    * [KARAF-276|http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-276] - upgrade to pax-url 1.2.1